snippet.title: Cities: Skylines - Concerts, Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Get Cities: Skylines - Concerts TODAY: http://tinyurl.com/ybo6bwj8
Concerts lets players control every aspect of making their metropolises more musical. From new festival ground buildings to city ordinances for driving ticket sales, Concerts goes beyond the music for players to tailor their cities’ festivals to fit their mood with music and images from musical acts NESTOR, Elijah MOTi, and Lily La Roux.

Throw up your horns and bang your heads in Cities: Skylines - Concerts
